	"<div class=\"slide slide-280 master-content\">\n<div class=\"slide-wrapper \">\n\t\n<h1>Installing Sass</h1>\n\n\n<h2>Applications</h2>\n\n\n<div class=\"slide-content\">\n\t<!-- slide-content -->\n\n<p>There are many applications that’ll help you get up to speed quickly.  Most of them are paid apps.  Here are a couple:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://incident57.com/codekit/\" target=\"_blank\">CodeKit</a> (Mac only)</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://compass.kkbox.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Compass.app</a> (Mac, Windows, Linux)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/andrew/node-sass\" target=\"_blank\">node-sass</a> (Mac, Windows, Linux)</li>\n</ul>\n<!-- /slide-content -->\n</div>\n\t<footer>\n\t\t<span class=\"presentation-title\">Web Developer's Workflow</span>\n<span class=\"presentation-pagination\">280</span>\n\n\t</footer>\n</div>\n\n</div>",
