	"<div class=\"slide slide-282 master-content\">\n<div class=\"slide-wrapper \">\n\t\n<h1>Installing Sass</h1>\n\n\n<h2>Node</h2>\n\n\n<div class=\"slide-content\">\n\t<!-- slide-content -->\n\n<p>Sass via node-sass depends on Node</p>\n<pre class=\"CodeMirror CodeMirror-pre-rendered cm-s-blackboard\"><span class=\"cm-builtin\">npm</span> install <span class=\"cm-attribute\">-g</span> node-sass</pre>\n<p>or </p>\n<pre class=\"CodeMirror CodeMirror-pre-rendered cm-s-blackboard\"><span class=\"cm-builtin\">sudo</span> <span class=\"cm-builtin\">npm</span> install <span class=\"cm-attribute\">-g</span> node-sass</pre>\n<p>Run <code>node-sass</code> to check if it is installed correctly (and see help info).</p>\n<!-- /slide-content -->\n</div>\n\t<footer>\n\t\t<span class=\"presentation-title\">Web Developer's Workflow</span>\n<span class=\"presentation-pagination\">282</span>\n\n\t</footer>\n</div>\n\n</div>",
